{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make helmets legal requirement while riding a bicycle or scooter on public roads",
        "additional_details": "Wearing a helmet can save lives and reduce head injuries in the event of an accident. This could be called Riley's Law.",
        "background": "My brother Riley died following a fatal collision in 2021. I believe my brother would still be with us today if he was wearing a helmet. Make it a legal requirement to wear a helmet when you are on a bicycle or scooter. ",
